  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A merge puzzle inspired by slot machine symbols!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine replays to make bells, bells to make watermelons… and finally, stick red sevens together to aim for the rainbow seven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/32aa928aeb35a067eeddefd12513c96b.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/43b97e85d2825bfadf4742954e5a3489.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/3a8b74bce219d2f37f5b1c118a699338.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sticking red sevens triggers a bonus time, boosting your score multiplier for a certain number of turns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you combine more red sevens during that period, you might enter a loop!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use luck and skill to snatch high scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scores will be registered in Steam's rankings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a pop and cute, yet uniquely random merge puzzle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A merge puzzle inspired by slot machine symbols!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine replays to make bells, bells to make watermelons… and finally, stick red sevens together to aim for the rainbow seven!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/32aa928aeb35a067eeddefd12513c96b.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/43b97e85d2825bfadf4742954e5a3489.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2804960/extras/3a8b74bce219d2f37f5b1c118a699338.avif?t=1760114108\" width=600 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sticking red sevens triggers a bonus time, boosting your score multiplier for a certain number of turns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you combine more red sevens during that period, you might enter a loop!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use luck and skill to snatch high scores!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scores will be registered in Steam's rankings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a pop and cute, yet uniquely random merge puzzle.</p>",
